# Unreal Engine generated files. Source, Config, Content, and descriptor files
# remain trackable; these paths are recreated by UnrealBuildTool or the helper.
**/Binaries/
**/DerivedDataCache/
**/Intermediate/
**/Saved/
**/.vs/
*.target
*.modules
*.version
*.generated.h

# Unreal helper staging/package outputs. The helper recreates these from
# include/, src/native/, and examples/unreal/FastDis/Source.
Epic/
examples/unreal/FastDis/ThirdParty/fastdis/
examples/unreal/FastDisOrientationVerification/Plugins/
examples/unreal/FastDisOrientationVerification/Config/DefaultEngine.ini
examples/unreal/FastDisOrientationVerification/Config/DefaultInput.ini

# Unity generated files. Assets, Packages, ProjectSettings, and UserSettings
# can be tracked when a Unity project is added.
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
UserSettings/
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb.meta
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

